metadata.description:
Dain Yoon, born in South Korea and now based in New York City, is a classically trained fine artist. Dain has gained worldwide recognition and acclaim for her unique creative style and her stunning illusion paintings using her skin as the ultimate canvas. With her art, Dain explores the many multi-faceted ways to express a personâ€™s diversity. Dain's eyes in particular have always been a key object or primary focal point of her face paintings. 
Dain's art is heavily inspired by her personal experiences and her passion for exploring the human psyche. She often incorporates elements of surrealism and fantasy into her work, creating dreamlike landscapes that are both captivating and thought-provoking.
metadata.name: Visionary | By Dain Yoon
